package.name: Horde_Dav
package.summary: Horde library for WebDAV, CalDAV, CardDAV
package.description: This package contains all Horde-specific wrapper classes for the Sabre DAV library.

release.notes: * [jan] Fix empty collections if applications don't provide DAV methods (Bug #12275).

* [jan] Fix installation path of \Sabre\VObject\Document. * [rla] Add system share support for CalDAV (Request #12342). * [jan] Fix PUTing content from the input stream to the backend. * [jan] Update to SabreDAV 1.8.6.
* [jan] Fix synchronization with SOGo connector. * [jan] Update to SabreDAV 1.8.7/VObject 2.1.3.

* [jan] Update to SabreDAV 1.8.10. * [jan] Add Hungarian translation (Andras Galos <galosa@netinform.hu>). * [jan] Update to VObject 2.1.4. * [jan] Add Danish translation (Erling Preben Hansen <erling@eph.dk>).
* [jan] Fix synchronization with Mac Calendar application after adding events.
